# Pokeball Collector

 ![](data:image/*;base64,)

Main functions are written by JadonMing - [Github](https://github.com/JadonMing/Diamond-Hunter)

**Description:**

This is a 2D RPG game. The object of the game is to control a man around the screen, collect all pok√©balls in limited time to win. To achieve the goal, the player needs to find item axe, boat and avoid traps.

**Controls:**

- --Move: UP, DOWN, LEFT, RIGHT or W, A, D, S
- --Use items: SPACE
- --Pause: ESC
